    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I'd be in favor of requiring for Interface/ERC but optional for network and core. The purpose really is to force the authors to consider the adversarial aspects of privacy invasions and to spur the discussion. If there truly isn't any than a quick short sentence would be suffice I think.",
